    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intro</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After months at sea, a witch and her daughter seek refuge in an old house. A storm is brewing, and the dark winter is drawing near. But amid death, hardship, and isolation, there is still a glimmer of hope, in the form of a scruffy old cat, who makes a promis to guide and protect. Embark on an unforgettable journey with a young witch and her loyal companion as they travel through a world in search of a new home, during a time of growing uncertainty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197450/extras/e484cbaef9f5a9538dc97f82faef962a.poster.avif?t=1768764475\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197450/extras/e484cbaef9f5a9538dc97f82faef962a.webm?t=1768764475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197450/extras/e484cbaef9f5a9538dc97f82faef962a.mp4?t=1768764475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along the road, Mia and Mio travel from place to place in search of shelter. Meet quirky characters, and make small choices that shape how the story ends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ An emotional story about being different and finding hope in dark times</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ Travel through the wilderness in search of safety and rest</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ Engage in character-driven dialogue that unfolds the story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ A fresh take on storytelling, seen through the eyes of Mia and her cat, Mio</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ Explore a beautiful Nordic world illustrated in an atmospheric, hand-crafted style</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ Meet dozens of quirky and mysterious characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ Guide Mia through moral choices that influence how her journey unfolds</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197450/extras/a8647515f5e33d20ed4841af3076814f.poster.avif?t=1768764475\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197450/extras/a8647515f5e33d20ed4841af3076814f.webm?t=1768764475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197450/extras/a8647515f5e33d20ed4841af3076814f.mp4?t=1768764475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
